# Xcode (gui/) – keep project.yml + sources, drop build output and
# user-specific Xcode metadata. The .xcodeproj is regenerated from
# project.yml via `xcodegen generate` so it doesn't need to live in
# git either, but we DO commit it for now so a fresh checkout can
# `xcodebuild ... build` without needing xcodegen.
gui/build/
gui/dist/
gui/DerivedData/
gui/**/xcuserdata/
gui/**/*.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/
gui/**/.build/
gui/**/Packages/
